Title: Jack Meets Dennis
Plot: Liz reconnects with her ex-boyfriend Dennis, the last remaining pager salesman in New York. Meanwhile, Jenna and Tracy try to "enhance" their appearances for career reasons.
GuestStars: Dean Winters, Michael Blackson, Greta Cavazzoni, Teddy Coluca, Brian Stack, Katrina Bowden, Keith Powell, Lonny Ross, Rachel Dratch, Ali Reza
